name: eHealth, Inc.
description: eHealth, Inc. is a technology and health insurance company that operates an online marketplace for health insurance products. Founded in 1997, eHealth provides consumers and small businesses with information and access to a wide range of health insurance plans, including Medicare Advantage, Medicare Supplement, and individual and family health insurance plans. The company aims to simplify the health insurance shopping experience through its user-friendly web-based platform, which allows users to compare plans, obtain quotes, and enroll in coverage all in one place. eHealth has built a reputation for its commitment to customer service, offering personalized assistance through licensed insurance agents who guide consumers through the complexities of health insurance options. As a key player in the digital health insurance space, eHealth leverages technology and data analytics to enhance its offerings and improve user experience. The company’s mission is to empower consumers to make informed decisions about their health insurance, ensuring they find the best coverage for their needs at competitive prices. Additionally, eHealth continuously expands its network of insurance carriers to provide a diverse selection of plans to its clients, reflecting its dedication to meeting the evolving needs of the healthcare market.
